[5] France
Date: Fri 13 Jul 2018
Source: Outbreak News Today [edited]
http://outbreaknewstoday.com/france-reports-3rd-measles-death-2018/


Health officials in France have reported the 3rd measles fatality of 2018 in a 17 year old girl with impaired immunity, from the region of New Aquitaine. Overall, there has been a decrease in the number of new weekly cases, and they have stabilized, with an average of 40 reported weekly cases.

As of 8 Jul 2018, 2646 cases have been reported since 6 Nov 2017 from 85 departments. Twenty-two per cent of reported cases were hospitalized. eighty-nine per cent of measles cases occurred in the unimmunized or under-immunized.

[byline: Robert Herriman]

